# Project Vision

This project is a modern enterprise-grade e-commerce platform.

The goal is to build a scalable, maintainable and extensible online store capable of supporting future growth without architectural rewrites.

The project should support:

- Product catalog
- Categories
- Inventory
- Pricing
- Customers
- Authentication
- Orders
- Checkout
- Payments
- Shipping
- Promotions
- Reviews
- Search
- SEO
- Analytics
- Administration

The architecture must allow future integration with:

- ERP
- CRM
- Marketplace APIs
- Payment providers
- Logistics providers
- AI services

Business continuity is more important than development speed.

Every implementation should improve the project rather than simply complete a task.